gnutls_x509_crl_check_issuer(3)                                                                   gnutls                                                                   gnutls_x509_crl_check_issuer(3)

NAME
       gnutls_x509_crl_check_issuer - API function

SYNOPSIS
       #include <gnutls/x509.h>

       unsigned gnutls_x509_crl_check_issuer(gnutls_x509_crl_t crl, gnutls_x509_crt_t issuer);

ARGUMENTS
       gnutls_x509_crl_t crl
                   is the CRL to be checked

       gnutls_x509_crt_t issuer
                   is the certificate of a possible issuer

DESCRIPTION
       This function will check if the given CRL was issued by the given issuer certificate.

RETURNS
       true (1) if the given CRL was issued by the given issuer, and false (0) if not.

